                <note rend="inline" type="source">500.A15 a 1/316: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chairman of the American Delegation</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gibson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-06-24T19:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 24, 1927—7 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>10. Your No. 25, June 23, 7 p.m. The action which you suggest taking is in accord
                    with your instructions. I approve your supporting adoption of decision by
                    Conference along lines set forth.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
